            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-06-25 09:15:41" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to have responsibility for the care of someone, implying a somewhat official responsibility within a congregation</DefinitionShort>
